OL,3,CNew film sheds light on mental health
OL,4,Cin the Orthodox Jewish Community
OL,6,FA new film based in Manchester's
OL,7,FOrthodox Jewish Community aims to
OL,8,Fhighlight the mental-health issues
OL,9,Ffelt by many young people there as
OL,10,Fthey struggle to deal with the
OL,11,Fpressure to conform and succeed.
OL,13,F"Levi" tells the story of Levi, a
OL,14,FJewish youngster, who arrives home
OL,15,Ffrom studying at a Yeshiva, a
OL,16,Freligious school.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
