OL,3,CNew film sheds light on mental health
OL,4,Cin the Orthodox Jewish Community
OL,6,FDesperately unhappy, Levi is unable to
OL,7,Fcommunicate how he feels to his
OL,8,Ffamily. He would rather study to
OL,9,Fbecome an architect but feels he is
OL,10,Fletting his family down by wanting to
OL,11,Ftake a different path. Unable to
OL,12,Fexpress his feelings, he considers
OL,13,Ftaking his own life.
OL,15,FThe film is the brainchild of
OL,16,FManchester-based political podcaster
OL,17,FEli Hassell.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
