OL,3,CNew film sheds light on mental health
OL,4,Cin the Orthodox Jewish Community
OL,6,FHe says the idea came after he'd
OL,7,Fspoken to many people in the Orthodox
OL,8,FJewish community who were struggling
OL,9,Fwith their mental health.
OL,11,FEli said: "I want young people in the
OL,12,Fcommunity who are going through mental
OL,13,Fproblems to be able to watch this film
OL,14,Fand realise there is a way out.
OL,16,F"I've seen a lot of it, a lot of
OL,17,Fyounger people suffering with mental
OL,18,Fhealth and sometimes really bad cases,
OL,19,Ftalking about suicide, it's tough
OL,20,Fseeing this."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
