OL,3,CNew film sheds light on mental health
OL,4,Cin the Orthodox Jewish Community
OL,6,FEli says while the community is self
OL,7,Fsupporting, somewhere where everyone
OL,8,Fknows everyone else, that can also
OL,9,Fmean people can be apprehensive about
OL,10,Fsharing their problems in case others
OL,11,Ffind out.
OL,13,FIt means mental health issues can be
OL,14,Finternalised and get worse. And for
OL,15,Fyoung people like Levi in the film,
OL,16,Fwho have a very particular path mapped
OL,17,Fout for then by their family,
OL,18,Fexpressing how they feel can be very
OL,19,Fdifficult.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
