OL,3,CNew film sheds light on mental health
OL,4,Cin the Orthodox Jewish Community
OL,6,FRabbi Avrohom Yeshaya Goldman was a
OL,7,Fconsultant on the film.
OL,9,FAvrohom runs a 24-hour Jewish mental
OL,10,Fhealth helpline, based in Manchester.
OL,12,FHe says that within the Jewish
OL,13,Fcommunity, like the world at large,
OL,14,Fthere is a stigma around talking about
OL,15,Fmental-health. B
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
