OL,3,CNew film sheds light on mental health
OL,4,Cin the Orthodox Jewish Community
OL,6,FHe said: "It's so close the small
OL,7,FJewish community so whenever anyone
OL,8,Fstruggles, they feel that this might
OL,9,Fbe impact who I'm going to marry,
OL,10,Fmight impact my siblings, my family.
OL,11,FSo much so that a father or a sibling
OL,12,For a mother might feel that their
OL,13,Ffamily might be better off without
OL,14,Fthem."
OL,16,FHe thinks the film is 'phenomenal' and
OL,17,Fwill hopefully help to reduce the
OL,18,Fstigma around mental health.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
